			  	@shwouchk and Nova<br />
<br />
Hmm, I read your ideas, but I don't think they'll help the game. You still only think of liminting stuff or making the empire stronger. At the end the weak councils will suffer only more. If you make the empire too strong the #1 council will simply adapt and stay low in power. If the secure border against the empire e.g. is 100k all top players will stay below 100k, with the result that all other players have to stay below 50k. <br />
You have to realize, that the #1 councils are #1, because they have the ability to adapt to changes very quickly. <br />
As I said before, the only good thing you can do is to speed up the rebuilding process of weak players.			   <P align=right></P>
