<br />
the decay might actually lower the top power, but this is actually a good thing - because it WILL make weak players climb faster... right now, the top players have over 1M, where id guess the averege power is about 20k... with 50k guys being all in the top 100... if you bring the top players closer to the rest of the pack, it will be much easier to wear them down, and let me promise you that top councils will change much faster then they do now... <br />
<br />
If you disable seeing of of the planet's features,  (especially its resources..) IT will be much harder to go planet hunting, especially during the beginning of the game when spying is very unadvanced, and people have little money to spend on it... this will ensure a much longer time before a dominant council emerges, and it will be much less dominant then now, allowing for much more room for competition... it will also crate more diversity in the chosen, and top races, since spying abilities will be much more important...<br />
<br />
my last idea lets the bottom guys acquire superior weapons and thus enabling them to defeat the top guys.. this one best works together with option no. 1 (about the empire...)... but there is a lot to consider here (for instance, might not the top guys get even better waepons etc, and become truly invincible?) and this is the hardest to implement by far, I think, so im just throwing thoughts with this :D			   <P align=right></P>
