			  	Some things that work in other games that may help here.<br />
<br />
Limit Alliances to 4 players.  (Of course this won't limit blocks of alliances working together, but will limit those that can directly support each other to 4)<br />
Limit Blockades to war status only.  Blockading fleets must stay on blockaded planet for a specified time to enforce the blockade.<br />
Create a Scout mission for ships.<br />
Increase travel time for missions outside own cluster and have it incremental for each cluster.  ie, if you are in Yehl, missions in Yehl take the standard time, missions to Bagvarti take standard time +2, missions to Nun take standard time +4 and so on.<br />
Add a request intervention option in Empire Dipl that would allow council leaders in good standing to request the empire attack higher ranked councils who declared on them, with the same chance of success as request mediation. 			   <P align=right></P>
