			  	I like Ziu's suggestion of giving a bigger boost to the players rebuilding, and slowing down the build rates of the top players. That might help set up a sort of an equilibrium between all the players, making it so that the majority would stay in a set power range fighting on a pretty much even ground with each other, where your skill in ship combat comes in handy.<br />
