			    <HR color=#000000 SIZE=-1>
			  	Entropy is the effect of things becoming more disordered.  It has the label delta S and is always negative.  For this reason, it has also been nicknamed the arrow of time.  To reverse entropy is to give order where there was none and not lose energy.  Or for the process to be spontaneous.  It's the reason why that tech is so high.  To reverse Entropy is to control the essence of everything.  You can bring to order things that are meant to be disordered.  An eggshell will spontaneously transform from the shattered pieces.  Like watching a film in reverse.			   <P align=right></P>
